{"tid":2293193,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"爭拗授權票有效性 「深藍」會長腰斬西醫工會選舉","createTime":"2020-11-20T05:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T05:35:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"63f8647ab139b2c9ed4676c57b52d4e1dc34fe61","tid":2293193,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T05:35:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/253K3NELPJC53JXNQBMTEKUGEQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2F253K3NELPJC53JXNQBMTEKUGEQ%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=5729ec06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2F253K3NELPJC53JXNQBMTEKUGEQ%2F&h=a2131c75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/253K3NELPJC53JXNQBMTEKUGEQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n爭拗授權票有效性<br />\n「深藍」會長腰斬西醫工會選舉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2JC2uPYSV04E6i8iIzVgYQET92E=/720x462/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7GQXIDAGAFDKRO6K2YSUHPFZ4I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2JC2uPYSV04E6i8iIzVgYQET92E%3D%2F720x462%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7GQXIDAGAFDKRO6K2YSUHPFZ4I.jpg&h=8615e777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊超發<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】選前已爆出風波的西醫工會，昨午舉行周年大會及選舉。歷任會長18年、立場「深藍」的楊超發面對副會長梁漢輝挑戰，梁漢輝大爆工會賬目不清，又多年無報稅，早前被楊超發強行暫停職務。據了解，選舉競爭激烈，約有574張授權票，為創會以來最多，惟會上就授權票有效性多番爭拗，最終會長楊超發以情況混亂為由取消大會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被質疑未有解釋理據<br />\n<br />\n擁有逾1,500名會員的西醫工會，過去甚少會員親身出席投票，因此授權票是決勝關鍵。去年只有約64張授權票，今屆因多個職位都。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n競逐會長一職的梁漢輝表示，會。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n競逐連任義務司庫的陸偉亮亦批評，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n對於今次大會取消原因及授權票爭拗等問題，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n選舉前梁漢輝已批評，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》又報道，西醫工會自成。。。。。。"}]}